        <h4>General:</h4>
        <p>Title your document or image with FirstNameLastName__TitleOfPiece__Genre</p>
        <p>Ex: ScottFitzgerald__TheGreatGatsby__Novel</p>
        <h4>Writing:</h4>
        <p>Please upload a google doc and give editors commenting access.</p>
        <p>Writing submissions are capped at 1000 words. For pieces longer than this, you may submit an excerpt.</p>
